# UI Styling Rules

## Tailwind CSS Usage

- Use **only Tailwind CSS utility classes**.
- Use the global styles file at `@/styles/index.css` for base styles.
- Use the helper **`cn`** function from `@/shared/utils` for conditional class names.

## Shadcn UI Components

- Import components from `@/shared/components/ui`.
- Available components:

```
tooltip, toggle-group, toggle, textarea, tabs, table, switch, spinner, sonner, slider, skeleton, sidebar, sheet, separator, select, scroll-area, resizable, radio-group, progress, popover, pagination, navigation-menu, menubar, label, kbd, item, input-otp, input-group, input, hover-card, form, field, empty, dropdown-menu, drawer, dialog, context-menu, command, collapsible, checkbox, chart, carousel, card, calendar, button-group, button, breadcrumb, badge, avatar, aspect-ratio, alert-dialog, alert, accordion
